parameters: -------Several years later
シーン-異教徒END
シーン-異教徒END
回想セーブ 異教徒バッドエンド
\n< Serena >Ohhh!!

\n< Male >Ohhh... Ugh, so this is the condition of the
beautiful princess of Venus...
\n< Serena >Ugh... Ahh...!

\n< Male >I decided from the moment I saw you. I
decided from the moment you were
revealed to that Battabayar guy.
\n< Male >I will make you mine.
\n< Male >Someday, like this, I will...! Hmph!!
\n< Serena >Ahhhh!
\n< Male >Hahaha! It took five years but...!

\n< Male >Your... this place is better than I imagined!
I'm endlessly interested! My blood won't
stop flowing!

\n< Male >Are all the women in the northern region
like this?

\n< Male >This battle is already coming to an end.
Once the grasslands unite, the next step
is to rampage through the imperial
territory...

\n< Male >It might be interesting to try invading
the northern region by passing through
the Great Forest this time... don't you
think?
\n< Serena >Ahh... Ah...! Ugh...!
\n< Child >Ee-ji-...
\n< Serena >!! You...! Why did you come back...!

\n< Subordinate >General, we have captured the brats of
Battubayar.

\n< Male >Good work. Hehehe. They may resemble their
mother, but they are an ugly bunch. Did
the blood of Battubayar come out strong?

\n< Male >Hm... Is someone missing? Wasn't there an
insolent brat of a certain age?
\n< Subordinate >I'm sorry. They resisted.
\n< Serena >Ahhh...!

\n< Male >If you haven't let them escape, it doesn't
matter.
\n< Male >Anyway, we're doing the same thing.
\n< Subordinate >Well then.
\n< Serena >S-Stop it!
\n< Male >Hmmm?
\n< Serena >Please... the children, at least...!

\n< Male >They're not just brats we made as we pleased,
right? The women brought here as spoils
of war...

\n< Serena >The children are innocent... Everyone,
everyone is a good child...!

\n< Serena >The only sparkle I obtained... in the midst
of this life as a captive...

\n< Child >Eiji... Why are you naked? What are you doing?
Who is that man?

\n< Serena >Th-This is... ngh! It's... it's nothing... at
all...!
\n< Child >Eiji? Your face is red...
\n< Serena >It's okay, it's oka...nggh!...so...!

\n< Male >Hmph. Even though they're just kids, at that
age, they should be a bit more
observant.

\n< Male >It seems like the seed wasn't good. Or
maybe it's the education? You were fond
of cats, right?
\n< Serena >Shut up... Shut up...!

\n< Male >Don't worry. My seed is of better quality
than Batbayar's. I'll make sure to
impregnate you with a replacement soon.
Something even better.

\n< Male >If you're going to breastfeed anyway,
wouldn't it be better to have strong
children made from excellent seeds?
\n< Male >Take them with you.
\n< Child >Ei-jiiiiiiiiiiii!!!
\n< Serena >Aaaaaahhhhh!!!

\n< Male >Look, don't cry, don't cry. This is also a
custom of the chaotic world. It's the
fate of the grasslands.
\n< Serena >Ugh!

\n< Male >Good women have the obligation to give birth
to stronger children. They have a
responsibility.

\n< Male >Leaving weak seeds is a sin against our
ancestors.
\n< Serena >You...! How dare you...! How dare you...!

\n< Male >Hahaha, that's right, those eyes. The eyes of a
mother who had her child taken away. I
wanted to see those eyes of yours!

\n< Male >I'll quickly find a replacement. You just
keep giving birth to my children under
my rule.

\n< Male >Give birth to a detestable boy. A child who
will be the enemy of my child.

\n< Male >It's our child. They will grow up to be
smart and strong. Those children will
invade your homeland...

\n< Male >Isn't your heart leaping just from dreaming?
Hahaha, I'm looking forward to it. I'm
really looking forward to it...
Scene_Recollection.prototype.rngd_exit_scene();
